sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as React UI
  participant API as ResourceLibrary.API
  participant CQ as MediatR CQRS
  participant SVC as AiAudioService
  participant FW as Faster-Whisper

  UI->>API: POST /api/aiAudio/asr (multipart: file, language?)
  API->>CQ: TranscribeAudioCommand
  CQ->>SVC: TranscribeAsync(stream, language?)
  SVC->>FW: POST /audio/transcriptions (OpenAI-compat)
  FW-->>SVC: { text, language }
  SVC-->>CQ: AsrResult
  CQ-->>API: TranscribeResponseDto
  API-->>UI: 200 { text, language }
